---
import Base from "@layouts/Base.astro";
import Nav from "@components/Nav.astro";
import Button from "@components/Button.astro";
import Card from "@components/Card.astro";
import FAQ from "@components/Landing/FAQ.astro";
import Footer from "@components/Footer.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Eco Clean Professional Service"
  description="Expertly Crafting Exceptional Spaces, Enriching Lives Through Thoughtful, Sustainable Transformation with Our Commitment to Eco-Friendly Practices and Community Enhancement"
  image="image/og-image.jpeg"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <main
    class="px-4 pb-4 space-y-2 md:h-[70vh] bg-[url('/images/bg.jpg')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat flex flex-wrap items-start" style="background-image: url('/images/power-bg.png');"
  >
    <Nav />
   

        <div data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="800"
          class="md:px-20  px-4 flex flex-col  w-full flex-1 items-center justify-center tracking-widest "
        >
            <h1 class="font-urbaneRounded-medium text-center text-5xl md:text-7xl   text-[#89d232] mb-1">
              POWER WASHING
            </h1>
            <p class="font-urbaneRounded-light text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl max-w-[560px] grid text-white my-6 leading-10 uppercase">
                Revitalize Your Surfaces with
                Eco-Friendly Precision
                


            </p>
          
        
        </div>
    
   
  </main>

  <section class="pt-10 pb-8 px-8 md:pt-28 md:pb-20 md:px-20 lg:px-44 flex flex-col gap-4">
    <div class="flex-1 mt-5 md:mt-0 flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row gap-4">
<div class="flex-1">

    <p class="text-[#85cd32] font-urbaneRounded-medium mb-10">
        PRESSURE CLEANING SERVICES, HUNTINGTON BEACH, CA
      </p>
      <h3 class="font-degular-semibold text-4xl md:text-6xl max-w-[480px]  text-[#1d6292]  mb-10">POWER WASHING PERFECTION WITH
        ECO CLEAN</h3>
      <p class="font-degular-semibold max-w-[460px]  text-xl mb-10">Revitalizing Surfaces While Caring for Nature: Our Eco Clean Power Wash Promise Delivers Superior Cleanliness with Environmental Respect, Balancing Effective Results with Ecological Sensitivity</p>
</div>
         
<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-14">
    <img src="/images/power-2.png" class="w-full" />
   
</div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="font-urbaneRounded-medium  text-lg">Eco Clean’s power washing services offer the ultimate cleaning solution, expertly removing the toughest dirt, grime, and buildup to rejuvenate the beauty and integrity of your property’s exterior. Our eco-conscious approach combines advanced cleaning methods with environmentally sustainable practices, ensuring a comprehensive clean that’s both powerful and planet-friendly. From the cozy nooks of residential homes to the expansive facades of commercial buildings, we tailor our services to meet the specific needs of each property, ensuring optimal results every time.
            <br/>
            <br/>


            For residential areas, we focus on enhancing curb appeal, carefully treating driveways, sidewalks, siding, and decks to remove unsightly stains and wear, restoring homes to their pristine condition. In commercial spaces, our power washing services are geared towards maintaining a professional and welcoming appearance for clients and employees, with special attention to parking lots, walkways, and building exteriors.
            <br/>
            <br/>
            
            Our team of power washing experts is equipped with the latest technology, capable of eradicating even the most stubborn dirt and grime, ensuring a lasting clean that enhances the visual and structural integrity of your property. By choosing Eco Clean, you invest in a service that values the longevity and health of your assets, embracing a partnership that stands for excellence and eco-responsibility. Let us transform your property with our powerful, sustainable power washing services, creating exteriors that gleam with cleanliness and care.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section
  class="md:px-20 lg:px-44 px-8 md:pt-36 md:pb-28 pt-16 pb-12 text-white text-center bg-[url('/images/bg-pattern-2.jpg')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat "
>
  
  <h2 data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="50" class="text-4xl md:text-6xl  font-degular-semibold mb-7">CONTACT US NOW TO SCHEDULE</h2>
  <div class="w-full flex justify-center items-center ">
    <Button
      text="REQUEST A QUOTE"
      link="quote"
      classes="text-white py-3 px-11 border-white font-urbaneRounded-medium transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:text-primary hover:border-white"
    />
  </div>
</section>
  

  <section class=" md:px-20 lg:px-44 px-8 py-16 bg-[#EEFAF5] " >
    <p class="text-[#85cd32] font-urbaneRounded-medium" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="600">
        HIGH-PRESSURE ECO CLEANING, HUNTINGTON BEACH, CA
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl text-[#1d6292] font-degular-semibold mb-2" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="700" data-aos-delay="50">WHY CHOOSE ECO CLEAN</h2>
    <p class="font-urbaneRounded-medium mb-16" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="700" data-aos-delay="100">
        Experience the Eco Clean Difference: Precision Power Washing Tailored to Your Specific Needs, Delivering Impactful and Lasting Results with a Commitment to Eco-Friendly Practices
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 grid-cols-1 gap-8 justify-between ">
      <div  data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay='100' class="min-h-[100%]" >

        <Card classes="min-h-[100%]"
          image="/images/power-3.png"
          title="Eco-Friendly Solutions"
          description="At Eco Clean, we prioritize the health of our planet while delivering knockout results. Our environmentally safe cleaning agents and methods effectively combat dirt and stains without compromising the earth’s well-being. This approach ensures a powerful clean that supports sustainability, aligning with our commitment to ecological responsibility."
        />
      </div>
      <div  data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay='200' class="min-h-[100%]" >
     

        <Card classes="min-h-[100%]"
          image="/images/power-4.png"
          title="Advanced Technology"
          description="Leveraging the latest in power washing technology, Eco Clean eradicates stubborn stains, mold, and mildew, rejuvenating your property’s look. Our equipment is designed to deliver high efficiency and effectiveness, ensuring a deep clean that enhances your property's aesthetic and structural integrity."
        />
      </div>
      <div  data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay='300' class="min-h-[100%]" >


        <Card classes="min-h-[100%]"
          image="/images/power-5.png"
          title="Expertise in Action"
          description="Our technicians are more than cleaners; they're trained professionals who understand the nuances of power washing. With expertise in various surfaces and environments, they assess and implement the best cleaning strategies, guaranteeing optimal results. Their skillful execution ensures that every job is done right, with attention to detail and respect for your property."
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>






  <div class="bg-[url('/images/power-6.png')] w-full  md:-mt-48  bg-fixed bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat ">
    <section
    class="space-y-8 md:px-20 lg:px-44 px-8   pb-16 pt-16 md:pt-48 text-center text-white  "
  >
    <div class="p-4 md:p-8 text-center flex flex-col items-center ">
      <p class="font-urbaneRounded-medium mb-6">BIODEGRADABLE CLEANING SOLUTIONS, HUNTINGTON BEACH, CA</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl  font-degular-semibold max-w-[800px] text-center md:leading-[4rem] mb-8">
        LET’S MAKE YOUR PROPERTY SHINE

      </h2>
      <p class="font-urbaneRounded-light max-w-[1100px]">
        Ready to transform your exterior spaces with powerful, eco-friendly cleaning? Contact Eco Clean today for a consultation and see how our power washing services can make your property look its best. It’s time to give your surfaces the clean they deserve and the protection they need to withstand the elements and time.


      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex justify-center items-center ">
      <Button
        text="REQUEST A QUOTE"
        link="quote"
        classes="text-white border-white font-urbaneRounded-medium transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:text-primary hover:border-white"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
  </div>




  <section class="pb-10 px-10 mt-20 md:pb-28 md:px-20 lg:px-44 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-14 mt-6 md:mt-0">
        <img src="/images/power-7.png" class="w-full" />
        <Button data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="20"
        text="CONTACT US"
        link="/services"
        classes="self-start text-[#1d6292] text-xl px-11 py-3 border-[#1d6292] font-urbaneRounded-medium  transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-primary hover:text-white hover:border-primary"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1">

        <p class="text-[#85cd32] font-urbaneRounded-medium mb-8">
            ENVIRONMENTALLY SAFE WASHING, HUNTINGTON BEACH, CA
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-degular-semibold text-4xl md:text-6xl max-w-[560px]  text-[#1d6292]  md:leading-loose mb-8">OUR POWER WASHING SERVICES


          </h3>
          <p class="font-degular-semibold max-w-[500px]  text-xl mb-8 ">Extensive Power Washing Services Spanning from Residential Homes to City Streets, Guaranteeing Thorough Cleanliness with a Sustainable Approach, Reflecting Our Dedication to Environmental Excellence

          </p>
            <p class="font-urbaneRounded-medium  max-w-[520px]">
                Our power washing services at Eco Clean encompass a wide range of applications, ensuring every corner of your property shines with cleanliness and care. In the residential realm, we specialize in transforming home exteriors, where years of accumulated dirt and discoloration meet their match against our powerful cleaning methods. Siding, roofs, and garages receive a thorough cleanse, significantly enhancing your home’s curb appeal and overall aesthetic. In the commercial sector, our expertise extends to facades that demand a professional and immaculate appearance. We help businesses convey quality and attention to detail through spotless exteriors, from brick walls to glass windows. Furthermore, our service portfolio includes the meticulous cleaning of concrete and asphalt surfaces, such as parking lots, driveways, and walkways, where we remove hazards and restore aesthetic appeal. Decks and patios also benefit from our refresh services, where we eliminate grime and weather-related wear, revitalizing these outdoor living spaces for enjoyment and relaxation.


            </p>
    </div>
    
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section id='faq' class=" md:px-20 lg:px-44 px-8  py-16 text-center bg-[#EEFAF5] ">
    <div class="flex items-center flex-col" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800" data-aos-delay="120">
      <p class="text-[#85cd32] font-urbaneRounded-medium mb-4">SUSTAINABLE HIGH-PRESSURE WASH, HUNTINGTON BEACH, CA </p>
      <h2 class=" text-[#1d6292] font-degular-semibold text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-6">FAQS</h2>
      <p class="font-urbaneRounded-medium max-w-[1000px] text-center mb-16">
        Diving Deep to Address Your Queries: Providing Comprehensive Clarity and Demonstrating Our Expertise with Detailed, Insightful Answers to Foster Understanding and Trust in Our Exceptional Cleaning Services
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-left flex flex-col gap-2">
      <FAQ
        question="What makes Eco Clean different from other cleaning services?"
        answer="Eco Clean stands out through our commitment to eco-friendly practices, using only safe, sustainable products, and methods. Our team's expertise and passion for environmental stewardship ensure a high-quality, green cleaning experience."
      />
      <FAQ
        question="Can Eco Clean handle both residential and commercial cleaning jobs?"
        answer="Absolutely! Eco Clean is equipped to handle a wide range of cleaning tasks, from cozy residential spaces to large commercial properties. Our flexible services are designed to meet the unique needs of each client, ensuring top-quality results every time."
      />
      <FAQ
        question="How does Eco Clean contribute to environmental sustainability?"
        answer="We prioritize the use of environmentally friendly cleaning agents and methods, reduce waste, and promote recycling and responsible disposal practices. Our aim is to minimize our ecological footprint while delivering exceptional cleaning services."
      />
      <FAQ
        question="What can I expect during an Eco Clean service visit?"
        answer="Expect professional, courteous, and efficient service from our team. We’ll arrive on time, conduct a thorough cleaning as per your specific requirements, and leave your space spotless and refreshed, all with the least environmental impact possible."
      />
      <FAQ
        question="Do you use eco-friendly products for all types of cleaning services?"
        answer="Yes, we are committed to using eco-friendly products for all our cleaning services. Whether it's carpet cleaning, power washing, or window cleaning, we ensure that our products are safe for the environment, your family, and your pets, aligning with our mission to provide sustainable and effective cleaning solutions."
      />
      <FAQ
        question="How often should I schedule cleaning services with Eco Clean?"
        answer="The frequency of cleaning depends on various factors, including the type of space, its usage, and personal preferences. For residential spaces, we recommend professional cleaning every 6 to 12 months, while commercial spaces might need more frequent services. We can work with you to create a customized cleaning schedule that meets your specific needs and ensures your space remains pristine."
      />
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="space-y-8 md:px-20 lg:px-44 px-4 py-4 md:pt-16 bg-[#308ed0]"><Footer/></section>
  <!-- <Footer /> -->
</Base>
